Gertrude Robinson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gertrude_Robinson 0 Gertrude Robinson (7 October 1890 – 19 March 1962) was an American actress of the silent era. She appeared in 164 films between 1908 and 1925. She was born in New York, New York and died in Hollywood, California.
